13. 1604, 27 Martii, Sibenici.

In Curia episcopali presbyter Georgius Despotovic parochus villae Murtarii et Betinae dioceseos Sibenicensis —interrogatus — cofirmavit et subscripsit characteribus glagoliticis:

Ja don Juraj Despotovic potvrdjujem te rici jesu zgora pisane.
